Heat oil in large deep skillet on medium-high heat. Add chicken; cook 7 min. or until cooked through, stirring occasionally. Mix broth, dressing and flour until well blended; gradually add to chicken, stirring constantly. Bring to boil. Reduce heat to medium-low; simmer 3 min. Add tortillas; stir to combine. Sprinkle with cheese; cover. Simmer 3 to 5 min. or until cheese is melted. Top with salsa.